  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7f62eac70c114d5c2a9d59e1ddff2c65, type: 3}
  m_Name: DemonData_K_vis
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: LSG::LSG.DemonData_K_vis
  demonName: K'vis
  canDateDemonMultipleTimes: 0
  introDialogue: '"Biceps'', you think as the confused figure stands up from within
    the circle. ''Green biceps'', you think, as you stare at the mighty orc woman
    in front of you.  One strap of her smithing apron falls off a shoulder as she
    looks around.


    ""What is this, my time to get reborn in another world to
    be the hero?  %#@ that.  Pipsqueak, can''t you tell Orcs and Oni apart?""  she
    grumbles."'
  minimumPowerLevel: 10
  maximumPowerLevel: 20
  outcome: "\"She takes your kitchen knives for sharpening\n\nYou learn which symbol
    in the complicated satanist summoning book means \"\"orc\"\", and does not, in
    fact, mean \"\"imp\"\"\tYour knives are temporarily missing\""
  boon: Gain 1 Rizz
  bane: 'The next summoning, the suit images on the white cards and their power counter
    are invisible. '
  boonBaneDialogue: K'vis's Curse has veiled the White pages of the Necronomicon.
  dateOutcome: '"Getting dragged to a gym wasn''t your first idea for a date, but
    getting sweaty with K''vis is an experience you wouldn''t trade for anything. 
    She''s a hit with the other gym-goers, and you get roped into a video with a
    creator who went by ''leanbisonpattie''.  You have to explain that ''going viral''
    is a good thing to the Orc, but you''re not sure she gets it.


    Still, she
    seemed interested by the idea of a factory tour, so maybe you can get a second
    date out of the whole thing."'
